  "title": "Senior Engineer - Mfg Facilities/SCEM (MFG Industry/Loyang Area)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Develop, implement, and continuously improve Facility policies and management system.</li>\n  <li>Lead a team of technical specialist in the Operation and Maintenance of Facility System.</li>\n  <li>Manage contractors and ensuring safety, quality workmanship and on-time completion.</li>\n  <li>Condition Based Monitoring and improvement plans.</li>\n  <li>Energy and Water Efficiency opportunities assessment and improvement plans.</li>\n  <li>Capital investment plans, project planning and timely implementation.</li>\n  <li>Adhoc duties assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/Degree in Engineering with relevant experience.</li>\n  <li><strong>Singapore Certified Energy Manager (SCEM) is a must.</strong></li>\n  <li>Good leadership, communication, and negotiation skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong team player and result orientated.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>5 days work week</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Manufacturing Industry</strong></p>\n<p><strong>East Area/Loyang</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants, please forward a detailed resume and email to <strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p>\n<p>License No: 06C3745</p>\n<p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Singapore Certified Energy Manager, SCEM, Energy Manager</p>",
